{"word":"ἀλεωρή","slug":"ἀλεωρή","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἀλεωρή</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:ἀλέομαι'><el>ἀλέομαι</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li750'><b>1. </b><i>avoidance, escape</i>, <b><a href='S:Iliad'>Il.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b><a href='S:cum'>c.</a> <a href='S:genitive'>gen.</a> <i>a means of avoiding, a defence</i> or <i>shelter from</i> <el>δηΐων ἀνδρῶν</el> <b><a href='S:Iliad'>Il.</a></b>: <a href='S:absolute, absolutely'>absol.</a> <i>a defence</i>, <b><a href='S:Iliad'>Il.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}